ne">$ hexo deploy （可简写为<span class="string">&quot;hexo d&quot;</span>）</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>详细信息：<a href="https://hexo.io/docs/one-command-deployment.html">部署</a></p>]]></content>
      
      
      
